  </div>

  <div class="section -green -padding-s bizdev-section" id="values">
    <div class="container values list">
      <h2>Why join Enhancv?</h2>
      <div class="row list-item">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
          <p class="value-heading bullet"><span>No traditional corporate hierarchies</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
          <p class="value-heading bullet"><span>Everyone around you is deeply involved and ready to help &amp; empower you</span></p>
